content.rendered:
Directed by Satram Ramani

Written by Mudassar Aziz. Sasha Singh

Cast Sonakshi Sinha (Saira Khanna). Huma Qureshi (Rajshree Trivedi). Zaheer Iqbal (Zoravar Rehmani). Mahat Raghavendra (Srikanth Sreevardhan). Shobha Khote (Rajshree’s Grandmother). Kanwaljeet Singh (Rajshree’s Father). Alka Badola Kaushal (Rajshree’s Mother). Sachin Shroff (Saira’s Brother). Niki Walia (Zoravar’s Mother (as Nikki Aneja Walia)). Danish Pandor (Viren). Dolly Singh (Meera / Saira’s Friend). Jimmy Shergill (Atul Chhabra). Swati Tarar (Roli Aunty). Jagat Rawat (Uncle / Mausaji). Isha Dhillon (Nidhi). Kapil Dev (Self). Shikhar Dhawan (Self). Chloe Driver (Plus Size Model). Kay Eluvian (Cecile). Sankalp Gupta (KD (Friend)). Seana Momsen (Roxanne). Karis Pentecost (Doctor). Clara Zoroddu (Client). Jamie Humphrey ((as a different name) (credit only)). Florbella Francisco-pedro (Mother (uncredited)). Al Groves (Father (uncredited)). Sinead Hegarty (Dancer (uncredited)). Cher Myra (Pub customer (uncredited)). Eve-Yasmine Saoud-Easton (Dancer (uncredited)). Moa Wikberg (Dancer (uncredited))

Languages Hindi

Producers Mudassar Aziz. Surabhi Bhatnagar. Armaan Memon. Kuldeep Ojha. Rahul Rawat. Sahil Singh. Ashwin Varde.

Production T-Series. Wakaoo Films.
